data.description: This spacious 3 bed/3.5 bath townhome is located in a great location, close to shopping & freeway.   Built in 2006, home features an open floor plan, lots of light, stainless steel appliances w/ new range & microwave, & large bedrooms with ensuite bathroom.   Enjoy Murray's great schools & low utilities.   High Speed Internet included with HOA.  All appliances are included as well as washer & dryer. This home will not disappoint!  Buyer to verify all info.
